{
  "$schema": "supported-markets-registry-v1",
  "_doc": "Consolidated source of truth for which markets each market-aware insight-wave plugin supports, and how. Read by cogni-docs doc-generate (Step 2d Markets Callout injection), doc-power (market-aware IS/DOES/MEANS), doc-hub (Working-across-markets subsection in plugin guides), doc-readme-root (ecosystem-level localized-for-Europe paragraph), and doc-audit (Check 15 Markets Callout Consistency). This is the canonical upstream registry. cogni-docs ships a local fallback projection at references/market-coverage.json — when this upstream file exists, generators prefer it; the fallback is the graceful-degradation path used when a repo has not yet landed the upstream consolidation.",
